songs.title: Anything Is Possible
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: All]
B-A-R-B-I-E
Together, forever
You and me

[Verse 1: Lauren & Camilla]
I can be anything I wanna be
If I can dream it I can do it, no one's stopping me
And I will, yea I will
And I know I can do it 'cus I got my friends
We'll go on a journey that'll never end
Yea, we will
We will

[Pre-Chorus: Dinah]
We can be anything we want

[Chorus: All]
Me and my girls! Yeah
It's our world, yeah
Anything is possible, we're unstoppable
Me and my girls!
B-A-R-B-I-E

[Verse 2: Ally & NormaniWe're dreaming big, I know we are
We've got it all, we'll be superstars
Yea we will, we will

We're looking good, we're feeling proud
Gonna stand up, gonna shout it out
Yea, we will
Yea, we will

[Pre-Chorus: Dinah]
We can be anything we want

[Chorus: All]
Me and my girls! Yeah
It's our world, yeah
Anything is possible, we're unstoppable
Me and my girls!
Let's go

[Bridge: All]
B-A-R-B-I-E
I've got all my girls with me
Barbie!
B-A-R-B-I-E
Together, forever
You and me

[Pre-Chorus: Normani & Ally]
If I can dream it, then I can do it
I've got my girls with me
There's nothing to it

[Chorus: All]
Me and my girls! Yeah
It's our world, yeah
Anything is possible, we're unstoppable
Me and my girls!

[Outro: All]
(B-A-R-B-I-E
Together, forever
You and me)
